                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Bailey</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San José</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-05-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 9, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Bailey reports that the Nicaraguan minister for foreign affairs has been
                    assassinated.)</p>
            </div>
